# .trivyignore
#
# List CVE or GHSA IDs here to suppress Trivy vulnerability findings.
# Each entry should be preceded by comments explaining the reason for ignoring
# and the acceptance date.
#
# Format:
#   # Reason: <justification for ignoring>
#   # Acceptance date: YYYY-MM-DD
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
#
# Example:
#   # Reason: Not exploitable in our configuration; no fix available.
#   # Acceptance date: 2025-01-01
#   CVE-2024-12345
